title: Keycap Digit Nine

adjectives: Denoting a quantity consisting of one more than eight and one less than ten
verbs: To determine the number (of objects in a group).

nouns: The cardinal number that is the sum of eight and one

One of 9 equal parts of a whole.
9 is the natural number following 8 and preceding 10.
A concept of quantity involving zero and units
Mathematical object used to count, label, and measure
A number is one of several related types of mathematical objects.

description: The number 9 on a square with rounded corners, designed to look like a keycap.
apple_vendor_description: The keycap digit nine emoji on Apple devices is presented as a clean, crisp numeral with a subtle, almost luminous sheen.  Rendered with Apple's characteristic glossy 3D shading and soft rounded edges, it feels substantial and easy to read.  This emoji clearly denotes the number nine, essential for ordering, counting, or marking progress in digital communication.
